    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p>",
