    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel lengths off your <strong>cucumber</strong> until you end up with a pile of cucumber ribbons</p><p>Peel and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1657642319682-x200.jpg",
