          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>grated garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) with your <strong>mayo</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a bowl and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1657642329940-x200.jpg",
