            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, transfer the mushrooms to a clean board and shred apart using two forks - this technique is known as 'pulling' – these are your <strong>spiced</strong> <strong>pulled mushrooms</strong></p><p>Remove the base of your <strong>living lettuce</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>living lettuce</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> and cut away the core, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>living lettuce leaves</strong> from the stem until you are left with a pile of leaves</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1657642376858-x200.jpg",
