          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1657642376858-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, load the <strong>toasted pittas</strong> with the <strong>spiced pulled mushrooms</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong> and <strong>cucumber ribbons </strong>– these are your <strong>pulled mushroom shawarmas</strong></p><p>Top the <strong>pulled mushroom shawarmas </strong>with a dollop of<strong> garlic mayo</strong> and serve with the <strong>chips </strong>and<strong> lettuce leaves</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
